{
  "stem": "9113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we were afraid maybe somebody is there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then he said-- then he recognized my voice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said-- I said, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He said, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, he-- he was-- he-- he-- when he ran away two days before, we were sure that he was killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Remember, I sung you the [INAUDIBLE] He were run away before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I said-- and I asked, [INAUDIBLE] where did you-- and he was a very rich kid at home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They left a fortune in Europe, I mean in that little town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That he was the-- the richest family in town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he said, Hyman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "His voice changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "His face changed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He was not-- he was not already the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, Hyman, we made a mistake that we escaped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We have no place to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Because I was already-- he went to his Polacks which they give him a fortune away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Everything was denied to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Nothing was given to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He said, now we have-- now we have to try something new.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we already five.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we walked, and we walked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We walked, and we stopped in the-- in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "A whole night, it was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were tired already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Then they say they're gonna pick that time in the-- in the woods, was-- we-- we had bread but we had no water, and we had no nothing else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Then we-- then we had to go to a place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We had to find a little place where this is a little water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It wasn't clean water to drink, but just water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "When we stopped in that little place, that was very early in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Maybe 5 or 6 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Then two-- then those four went to pick blueberries.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And I remained in this place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
